<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>SqlSessionFactory </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>用于创建</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SqlSession </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>对象，而</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SqlSession </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>用于操作数据库。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>SqlSessionFactory </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>对象的实例可以通过</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>
     SqlSessionFactoryBuilder </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>对象类获得</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt'> , </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>而</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt'> SqlSessionFactoryBuilder </span><span style='font-family:
     "Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>则可以从</span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> XML </span><span style='font-family:
     "Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>配置文件或一个预先定制的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> Configuration </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的实例构建出</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SqlSessionFactory </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的实例，每一个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> MyBatis </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的应用程序都以一个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SqlSessionFactory </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>对象的实例为核心 </span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>SqlSessionFactory</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>可以通过配置文件或者</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Java</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>代码来创建，并且可以被多个线程共享使用。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>SqlSessionFactory </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>是线程安全的，它一旦被创建，应该在应用执行期间都存在。在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>MyBatis</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>中，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>SqlSessionFactory</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>通常只需要被创建一次，并且可以在整个应用程序生命周期内重复使用。因此，它通常被设计为单例模式。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

12.0pt'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>            </span><span
style='color:#8064A2'>sqlSessionFactory</span> = new
SqlSessionFactoryBuilder().build(is);</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>            </span>SqlSession session = <span
style='color:#8064A2'>sqlSessionFactory</span>.openSession(ExecutorType.<span
style='color:#8064A2'>BATCH</span>);</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>        </span>} catch (IOException e) {</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>            </span>e.printStackTrace();</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>        </span>}</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>}</p>
